text: Glen Rock or Glenrock may refer to: ==Places== === Australia === *Glenrock, Queensland, a locality in the South Burnett Region, Queensland ===United States of America=== * Glenrock, Nebraska, an unincorporated community in Nemaha County * Glen Rock, New Jersey, a borough in Bergen County * Glen Rock, Pennsylvania, a borough in York County * Glen Rock, Virginia, a neighborhood in Norfolk County * Glenrock, Wyoming, a town in Converse County ==Railway stations== * Glen Rock–Main Line station, on New Jersey Transit's Maine Line * Glen Rock–Boro Hall station, on New Jersey Transit's Bergen County Line
